@baseUrl = http://localhost:8084

### Upload media (choose existing file path in your client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/media/upload?uploaderId=1&altText=sample-image&linkedPostId=1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### Get all media
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/media

### Link media to post
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/media/1/link?postId=1

### Update alt
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/media/1/alt?altText=updated-alt

### Delete media
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/media/1
